  "instructions": [
    "Heat the binchotan grill to 350°F.",
    "In a large tagine or Dutch oven, heat the coconut oil over medium heat. Add the chopped onions and cook until lightly browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the Massaman paste and cook, stirring constantly, for 1-2 minutes.",
    "Add the chicken to the pot and cook until browned on all sides, about 5-7 minutes.",
    "Add the diced tomatoes, chicken broth, dried apricots, pine nuts, salt, and black pepper to the pot. Stir to combine.",
    "Cover the pot and transfer it to the preheated binchotan grill. Smoke the tagine for 30-40 minutes, or until the chicken is cooked through and the sauce has thickened.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and lemon juice. Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
  ],
